{"tid":880514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大(粵語)FTV：加軍香港保衛戰77周年舉辦紀念儀式","createTime":"2018-10-28T18:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T23:03:15.000Z","uid":47714,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40158d1824f108bcb44f03cc5e3e271a81b6365c","tid":880514,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:02:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.fairchildtv.com/news.php?n=2a6b2bb7b736404be9af4fb373e53ba4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fairchildtv.com%2Fnews.php%3Fn%3D2a6b2bb7b736404be9af4fb373e53ba4&d=ovH9S1ofknESdWIPPMJb8%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=6a59b050\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fairchildtv.com/news.php?n=2a6b2bb7b736404be9af4fb373e53ba4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fairchildtv.com/images/data/news_video/news_60135.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fairchildtv.com%2Fimages%2Fdata%2Fnews_video%2Fnews_60135.mp4&d=ovH9S1ofknESdWIPPMJb8%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=262893f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fairchildtv.com/images/data/news_video/news_60135.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n77年前的今日加拿大派出近2千名士兵前往香港參加對抗日軍的保衛戰，皇家香港軍團協會安省分會今日舉辦香港保衛戰紀念儀式。<br />\n<br />\n為紀念1975名加拿大軍人在77年前，1941年10月27日被派遣到香港協助防守的英勇事跡，安省大多倫多地區的香港移民和退伍軍人組織，今日在萬錦市無名英雄紀念碑前舉辦香港保衛戰紀念儀式。各級政府和社區的代表出席活動並且獻上花圈致敬。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆果 皇家香港軍團協會<br />\n&ldquo;我們加拿大派過去的1975名士兵當中，現在由東岸至西岸，應該只有15位老兵在世，希望能夠將他們的事跡繼續傳遞下去。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n超過500名青年士兵在當年戰死疆場,永遠留在了香港。大多倫多地區的香港保衛戰紀念活動由4年前開始舉辦，增加對香港和本國軍隊歷史的了解。"},{"pid":"931ba1f49693e0713352e2432c82dd4a36218bb6","tid":880514,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:20:16.000Z","msg":"加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw個主播對眼化妝化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f563cccc26279503dafdb120107c94a1551a2ba","tid":880514,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T18:21:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},